name: Invitation of madness
description: Embrace insanity, embrace being not normal, embrace being at odds with the world. Embrace the fact that the universe is, most likely, as mad as we all are. It is a cosmic wonderland, and we are the cats. Even so, it is worth to venture into the void. True, it is horrifying, but it is probably also prettier than you think. And when has being horrifying stopped people from exploring?
